  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 70c970a7d9f7d414994564bd048e8a6d, type: 3}
  m_Name: UFO_Compelling_Repeated
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: KBTV.Runtime::KBTV.Dialogue.CallerDialogueTemplate
  Topic: {fileID: 0}
  Legitimacy: 3
  Priority: 2
  Length: 12
  IntroLines:
  - Text: Vern, I've been seeing the same craft for ten years. Same location. Same
      time of year. It's not random.
    Tone: 0
    Weight: 1
  - Text: This isn't my first sighting. It's my fourteenth. I've documented every
      single one.
    Tone: 9
    Weight: 1
  - Text: I know how this sounds, but I think they're watching me. Coming back to
      the same spot, year after year.
    Tone: 10
    Weight: 1
  DetailLines:
  - Text: Every October, between the 15th and 20th. Same triangular craft. Same flight
      pattern. I've mapped it.
    Tone: 0
    Weight: 1
  - Text: The first time I thought I was crazy. By the fifth time, I started keeping
      detailed records. Times, weather, witnesses.
    Tone: 0
    Weight: 1
  - Text: Last year I set up cameras. Three angles. Got forty minutes of footage
      before it disappeared.
    Tone: 1
    Weight: 1
  DefenseLines:
  - Text: Ten years of documentation, Vern. Photographs, video, journal entries.
      You can't dismiss a decade of evidence.
    Tone: 0
    Weight: 1
  - Text: I've had the footage analyzed. No signs of manipulation. Whatever this
      is, it's real.
    Tone: 0
    Weight: 1
  - Text: Other people in my area have seen it too. We've formed a group. Twelve
      witnesses over the years.
    Tone: 0
    Weight: 1
  AcceptanceLines:
  - Text: Thank you. Most people think I'm obsessed. Maybe I am. But I'm not wrong.
    Tone: 10
    Weight: 1
  - Text: That means more than you know. My family stopped believing me years ago.
    Tone: 0
    Weight: 1
  - Text: I knew if anyone would take this seriously, it would be you.
    Tone: 1
    Weight: 1
  ExtraDetailLines:
  - Text: I've noticed patterns in the timing. It correlates with certain astronomical
      events. I don't think that's coincidence.
    Tone: 0
    Weight: 1
  - Text: The last three appearances, there's been a hum. Low frequency. You feel
      it more than hear it. My equipment picked it up.
    Tone: 1
    Weight: 1
  - Text: I've reached out to researchers at two universities. One is interested.
      The other stopped returning my calls after I sent the footage.
    Tone: 7
    Weight: 1
  ExtraDefenseLines:
  - Text: I'm an engineer, Vern. I've spent my career solving problems with data.
      This data is undeniable.
    Tone: 0
    Weight: 1
  - Text: I've invited skeptics to my property during the observation window. Three
      have seen it themselves. Changed their minds.
    Tone: 0
    Weight: 1
  - Text: Whatever this is, it wants to be seen. It comes back to the same place.
      That's not random behavior.
    Tone: 9
    Weight: 1
  ConclusionLines:
  - Text: October's coming, Vern. If you want to see for yourself, I'll send you
      coordinates.
    Tone: 1
    Weight: 1
  - Text: Ten years I've been waiting for someone to take this seriously. Thank you.
    Tone: 0
    Weight: 1
  - Text: Keep watching the skies. Especially in October.
    Tone: 0
    Weight: 1
